  <brief_title>Predictive Value of Dynamic Combination of BNP and NGAL for the Prognosis of Patients With Sepsis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Predictive Value of Dynamic Combination of B-type Natriuretic Peptide and Neutrophil Gelatinase-associated Lipocalin for the Prognosis of Patients With Sepsis</official_title>
