  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Objective: to clarify the predictive value of brain natriuretic peptide (BNP) in combination
      with neutrophil gelatinase associated lipocalin (NGAL) for the prognosis of patients with
      sepsis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
